I haven't seen you two arrive together in a long time.

0:02:44.400,0:02:48.280
If only everyone in the palace could be
as harmonious as you two.

0:02:48.560,0:02:50.980
Sourire and I have always been harmonious sisters.

0:02:51.200,0:02:52.620
Because the weather is getting hotter,

0:02:52.620,0:02:54.840
His Majesty is planning to escape 
the heat in the Summer Palace.

0:02:54.980,0:02:56.620
We will depart in a few days.

0:02:56.720,0:03:00.660
You should organize who and what 
you want to bring with you beforehand.

0:03:00.940,0:03:02.180
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:03:06.500,0:03:07.940
Your Majesty,

0:03:08.240,0:03:11.420
The Empress Dowager has not been able to 
leave the palace since she became ill.

0:03:11.620,0:03:14.700
I would like to stay and attend Her Majesty.

0:03:14.920,0:03:18.000
I will fulfill my filial piety to
Her Majesty through attentive service.

0:03:18.780,0:03:21.080
I appreciate your filial thoughts.

0:03:21.720,0:03:23.620
I thank Your Majesty.

0:03:27.340,0:03:31.000
The Imperial Household Department has 
arranged everything as before.

0:03:31.500,0:03:33.860
His Majesty stays in The Peaceful Nine States.

0:03:34.280,0:03:36.700
Her Majesty stays in Peach Blossoms Haven.

0:03:36.920,0:03:40.020
Your Highness stays in Verdant Reading Hall.

0:03:42.240,0:03:44.200
Doesn’t Noble Lady An stay in Lush Blossoms Chamber?

0:03:44.200,0:03:46.020
Why did she walk that way?

0:03:46.040,0:03:47.880
Your Highness,

0:03:47.880,0:03:50.500
Lady An will live in Leisured Moon Chamber.

0:03:50.920,0:03:52.420
His Majesty says that

0:03:52.420,0:03:56.500
Lady An is close to Your Highness, so your residences

0:03:56.840,0:04:00.100
should be nearby so that you can take care of each other.

0:04:00.440,0:04:02.920
It is also near to His Majesty.

0:04:03.600,0:04:06.560
I have something else to attend to.
I will visit Lady An another time.

0:04:07.040,0:04:08.340
You may leave.

0:04:08.340,0:04:10.280
I bid Your Highness goodbye.

0:04:19.760,0:04:20.720
My Lady,

0:04:20.720,0:04:22.840
are you feeling sad about Lady Vertu?

0:04:23.760,0:04:25.980
Last year, Meizhuang was in the prime of His Majesty's favor.

0:04:25.980,0:04:28.980
But this year, Lingrong stays in Leisured Moon Chamber.

0:04:29.060,0:04:31.500
Household items remain the same, but occupants change.

0:04:31.840,0:04:33.620
I fear that once I go there,

0:04:33.760,0:04:36.000
it will sadden me.

0:04:36.860,0:04:39.640
It's kind of you to feel this way.

0:04:39.820,0:04:41.760
But you should understand, My Lady,

0:04:41.840,0:04:45.720
there are many concubines in the palace.

0:04:46.360,0:04:49.420
One may be favored today, and another one tomorrow.

0:04:52.880,0:04:54.340
It is not certain.

0:04:54.600,0:04:56.380
You care about Lady Vertu,

0:04:57.020,0:04:59.200
but you don’t need to feel sad about her.

0:05:00.540,0:05:01.620
Jinxi.

0:05:02.740,0:05:05.520
I always worry too much over such trifles.

0:05:06.640,0:05:09.920
My Lady, you are sentimental sometimes.

0:05:10.940,0:05:12.000
However,

0:05:12.000,0:05:14.740
only a kind and gentle person would feel this way.

0:05:14.960,0:05:16.880
Cruel people would never.

0:05:18.140,0:05:21.240
Your shortcoming is that you are too soft-hearted.

0:05:21.520,0:05:23.500
You have so much to care about.

0:05:24.400,0:05:25.700
Your Highness!

0:05:26.560,0:05:27.880
Your Highness!

0:05:29.100,0:05:31.200
Fourth Prince, come down! Come down here!

0:05:31.240,0:05:32.340
Be careful not to fall.

0:05:32.420,0:05:33.720
Come down here.

0:05:37.880,0:05:40.400
Peace to Your Highness.

0:05:41.060,0:05:42.540
Why did you climb up so high?

0:05:42.680,0:05:44.080
Aren't you afraid of falling?

0:05:44.080,0:05:46.700
Except for my maids, no one cares about me.

0:05:46.980,0:05:47.980
Silly boy!

0:05:48.860,0:05:50.960
I heard that Father came here, and

0:05:50.960,0:05:52.420
I want to pay my respects to him.

0:05:52.440,0:05:54.400
But I'm scared that he doesn’t want to see me.

0:05:54.400,0:05:56.160
So I climbed up on the rocks

0:05:56.180,0:05:58.440
hoping that I would see him.

0:05:58.860,0:06:00.220
You want to see your father?

0:06:00.220,0:06:01.740
I will bring you to visit him.

0:06:02.140,0:06:03.220
But today,

0:06:03.280,0:06:05.640
His Majesty is meeting officials in court.

0:06:05.780,0:06:07.560
I’m afraid he won’t finish anytime soon.

0:06:08.280,0:06:09.640
Why don't you go back?

0:06:09.640,0:06:11.680
When His Majesty is available,
I will take you to him.

0:06:11.680,0:06:12.620
All right?

0:06:12.620,0:06:13.800
I thank Your Highness!

0:06:13.800,0:06:16.060
I'll be happy just to see Father.

0:06:17.240,0:06:18.260
Go on.

0:06:20.040,0:06:22.340
Here, Your Highness, this is for you.

0:06:27.040,0:06:28.600
Your Majesty,

0:06:29.520,0:06:33.900
Nian Gengyao took advantage of military 
actions to claim false merits,

0:06:34.060,0:06:37.840
and secretly accepted bribes to arrange 
high-ranking posts for his subordinates.

0:06:38.380,0:06:42.840
His subordinates leaned on his power to act with impunity.

0:06:43.480,0:06:46.320
Nian Gengyao's household servant Wei Zhiyao

0:06:46.340,0:06:48.040
has been exceedingly arrogant.

0:06:48.280,0:06:49.740
When he came to Beijing,

0:06:49.740,0:06:52.200
all civil officials bowed to him

0:06:52.620,0:06:54.720
and all military officers knelt.

0:06:54.900,0:06:58.840
But Wei Zhiyao passed by sitting on his sedan
without even looking at them.

0:06:59.000,0:07:03.540
This demonstrates his arrogance and feelings of power.

0:07:04.140,0:07:04.840
Your Majesty,

0:07:05.320,0:07:08.540
Nian Gengyao exercises dominance over all the officials.

0:07:08.860,0:07:11.480
On the pretext of training the military,

0:07:11.540,0:07:14.640
he detains many children of officials in his encampment.

0:07:14.900,0:07:17.400
After Wang Yun, the General of North Sichuan retired,

0:07:17.660,0:07:21.500
Nian Gengyao ordered his son to serve in his own regiment:

0:07:21.500,0:07:24.420
requested in the name of service,
but truly held as a hostage.

0:07:24.640,0:07:27.000
This is how he forces officials to obey him.

0:07:27.080,0:07:27.780
Enough.

0:07:33.780,0:07:35.760
This matter is of paramount significance.

0:07:36.160,0:07:38.420
Let's end it here today.

0:07:38.740,0:07:43.380
Inform Zhang Tingyu and Longkodo to see me tomorrow.

0:07:44.040,0:07:45.480
You may leave.

0:07:46.660,0:07:48.480
I thank Your Majesty.

0:07:55.940,0:07:56.800
Your Highness.

0:07:57.020,0:07:58.420
Where is His Majesty?

0:07:58.720,0:08:01.900
His Majesty says that he is unable to dine with Your Highness.

0:08:02.300,0:08:04.000
Please dine without him.

0:08:04.400,0:08:05.540
What’s more,

0:08:05.540,0:08:07.820
His Majesty said he anticipates being very busy

0:08:08.100,0:08:10.620
and might not be able to accompany Your Highness.

0:08:12.420,0:08:14.080
Allow me to take my leave.

0:08:16.020,0:08:17.360
Stay away!

0:08:22.440,0:08:25.700
I carefully inquired of His Majesty's servants.

0:08:27.460,0:08:31.360
It turns out that Zhen Yuandao led an impeachment
against my brother and his subordinates.

0:08:32.560,0:08:34.780
His Majesty has ordered the Ministry of Justice

0:08:34.780,0:08:37.540
to seize the hundreds of thousands of taels
embezzled by Wei Zhiyao.

0:08:38.560,0:08:40.820
His Majesty said he gained his wealth 
only because of his master

0:08:40.940,0:08:44.120
and that my brother abused his position to fill his own pockets,

0:08:44.300,0:08:46.740
which overflowed into those of his subordinates.

0:08:48.420,0:08:50.540
His Majesty despises corruption most of all.

0:08:51.000,0:08:54.540
Why were they so careless as to provoke His Majesty?

0:08:55.340,0:08:57.800
Zhen Yuandao's mouth never stops causing trouble.

0:08:58.280,0:09:01.500
He wants to help his daughter, and so he is against me.

0:09:02.380,0:09:04.040
I don’t know whether His Majesty

0:09:04.700,0:09:06.140
will also turn his anger on my brother.

0:09:07.740,0:09:09.820
These are small matters among some subordinates.

0:09:10.020,0:09:12.060
General Nian surely wasn’t involved.

0:09:12.860,0:09:16.660
Formerly there were some brazen fools who
tried to impeach General Nian,

0:09:17.140,0:09:19.400
but they were all rebuked by His Majesty.

0:09:19.680,0:09:22.100
His Majesty always trusted my brother

0:09:22.520,0:09:24.660
and rebuked those who reprimanded him.

0:09:25.100,0:09:29.320
But this time His Majesty has sent people to investigate
whether my brother knew of Wei Zhiyao's corruption.

0:09:31.120,0:09:33.220
Does His Majesty suspect my brother?

0:09:33.460,0:09:34.120
Your Highness,

0:09:35.340,0:09:38.460
It is only normal that His Majesty inquires.

0:09:40.460,0:09:43.740
But my brother’s subordinates tried to
cover up for Wei Zhiyao.

0:09:44.080,0:09:45.400
How could they?

0:09:46.620,0:09:50.240
Now His Majesty thinks that my brother’s
subordinates formed a faction to shield one another.

0:09:50.480,0:09:52.820
That’s why His Majesty sends people to investigate.

0:09:55.180,0:09:56.080
No wonder …

0:09:58.660,0:10:01.220
No wonder why His Majesty doesn’t come these days.

0:10:03.100,0:10:05.400
I’m afraid he's also turned his anger on me.

0:10:06.200,0:10:07.800
Don’t be sad, Your Highness.

0:10:08.240,0:10:10.620
It is difficult for Your Highness to see His Majesty right now.

0:10:10.860,0:10:14.240
In the future, Your Highness should refrain
 from speaking about the Great General.

0:10:15.100,0:10:16.120
What can I do now?

0:10:17.840,0:10:19.540
Everyone can speak about it,

0:10:20.180,0:10:21.680
everyone but me.

0:10:22.660,0:10:23.820
Your Highness,

0:10:24.060,0:10:26.140
I think, the plan for now,

0:10:27.320,0:10:30.840
is to avoid making His Majesty angry with Your Highness.

0:10:33.000,0:10:34.760
Then, let Lady Cao speak for me.

0:10:34.780,0:10:35.900
It's not appropriate.

0:10:36.320,0:10:39.200
Noble Lady Cao is never in high favor with His Majesty.

0:10:39.520,0:10:41.800
She is also not at the center of His Majesty's heart.

0:10:42.160,0:10:43.440
I'm afraid ...

0:10:43.960,0:10:46.280
it's not appropriate for her to speak up.

0:10:46.460,0:10:47.760
If I can't speak for myself,

0:10:49.620,0:10:52.220
I will need someone to gain favor from His Majesty

0:10:52.760,0:10:54.660
and speak for me.

0:11:27.280,0:11:28.220
Your Majesty,

0:11:28.220,0:11:30.920
the missteps of Wei Zhiyao are small
compared to other matters.

0:11:31.040,0:11:32.440
My investigation clearly shows

0:11:32.440,0:11:35.660
Nian Gengyao used his family to seek
exorbitant profits through business.

0:11:35.900,0:11:37.260
Nian Gengyao's sons,

0:11:37.260,0:11:38.620
Nian Fu and Nian Bin,

0:11:38.620,0:11:40.880
falsified documents to take ownership of salt pools.

0:11:41.300,0:11:45.900
They have made a profit of more than one hundred seventy thousand taels in the last two years.

0:11:46.020,0:11:48.980
This is only "one hair of a bull's back"
compared to what they have done.

0:11:49.380,0:11:50.640
As Qing Dynasty's law prescribes,

0:11:51.100,0:11:55.360
generals and governors should communicate
in the format of a Counsel Letter.

0:11:55.920,0:11:58.220
But, without permission, Nian Gengyao sends Command Orders

0:11:58.260,0:12:00.720
to his subordinate generals and governors

0:12:01.100,0:12:02.920
in the tone of an emperor.

0:12:03.280,0:12:06.540
Nian Gengyao endowed publishing 
"Sir Lu Zhi's Memorials to Emperor Dezong"

0:12:06.720,0:12:09.940
and entreated Your Majesty to write a preface for the book.

0:12:10.600,0:12:12.140
However, several days ago,

0:12:12.160,0:12:14.980
on the pretext of saving Your Majesty the bother,

0:12:15.240,0:12:17.520
he wrote the preface himself

0:12:17.780,0:12:19.860
and published it to the people.

0:12:21.620,0:12:23.220
"For any officials under a monarch,

0:12:25.280,0:12:26.560
it’s easy to seek merit

0:12:28.520,0:12:29.620
but hard to achieve it.

0:12:30.680,0:12:31.940
Once achieved,

0:12:33.120,0:12:34.480
even harder to maintain it;

0:12:35.820,0:12:37.320
And if merit is maintained,

0:12:38.160,0:12:40.320
it is harder still to maintain it to the end.”

0:12:40.640,0:12:43.140
Moreover, if they err because of pride in their merits,

0:12:44.240,0:12:46.520
former favor will become disfavor.

0:12:47.620,0:12:51.140
These are all common feelings of men.

0:12:54.220,0:12:55.360
Send this to all.

0:12:56.860,0:13:00.140
Let him reflect on it.

0:13:00.680,0:13:01.340
Your Majesty,

0:13:02.000,0:13:03.680
Nian Gengyao's arrogant behavior

0:13:04.100,0:13:06.120
is an audacious act of rebellion against Your Majesty.

0:13:06.240,0:13:09.120
Nian Gengyao was one of my retainers.

0:13:11.040,0:13:12.620
He contributed much

0:13:13.440,0:13:15.780
to my accession and governance.

0:13:16.340,0:13:17.200
I don't

0:13:18.140,0:13:22.240
wish to cut off my relation with him.

0:13:22.720,0:13:23.340
Your Majesty,

0:13:23.960,0:13:25.060
it's time for noon tea.

0:13:25.760,0:13:26.760
Serve it.

0:13:27.740,0:13:30.240
Your Majesty, this is the latest Longjing tea.

0:13:30.380,0:13:31.560
Please have a taste.

0:13:31.740,0:13:32.360
Quiet.

0:13:32.760,0:13:34.080
You were not spoken to.

0:13:35.240,0:13:37.840
I beg Your Majesty's pardon.

0:13:39.600,0:13:40.760
Song Zhi ...

0:13:42.080,0:13:43.000
It's you.

0:13:43.300,0:13:46.700
I obey Her Highness Consort Flour's order 
to serve Your Majesty the tea.

0:13:52.120,0:13:53.660
This dress looks nice on you.

0:13:58.960,0:14:00.700
Allow me to take my leave.

0:14:00.780,0:14:02.180
Allow me to take my leave.

0:14:02.580,0:14:03.600
Proceed.

0:14:06.220,0:14:08.780
You said that Consort Flour sent you here.

0:14:21.220,0:14:22.440
Peace to Your Highness.

0:14:22.440,0:14:23.540
Greetings, ministers.

0:14:26.520,0:14:27.580
You may rise.

0:14:28.420,0:14:29.760
I thank Your Majesty.

0:14:34.880,0:14:36.460
Your Majesty, please have the tea.

0:14:56.040,0:14:57.040
Your Highness.

0:14:57.500,0:14:58.520
Your Highness,

0:14:59.140,0:15:00.540
it's been a while.

0:15:01.100,0:15:05.760
I believe Song Zhi will stay here today.

0:15:06.200,0:15:07.520
Your Highness can leave if you wish.

0:15:11.260,0:15:12.720
Thank you, Mr. Su.

0:15:13.060,0:15:15.120
Your Highness has a keen eye for beauty.

0:15:15.420,0:15:18.620
That's why His Majesty appreciates Song Zhi.

0:15:53.800,0:15:56.140
Your Highness, you haven't slept yet?

0:16:01.240,0:16:04.040
In the past, Lady Cao and Concubine Beauté
were seeking my support

0:16:05.320,0:16:06.920
and I aided in their promotion.

0:16:10.260,0:16:13.100
But to send a woman to His Majesty's bed ...

0:16:15.720,0:16:17.320
It's the first time.

0:16:19.160,0:16:21.000
Your Highness had your reasons to do so.

0:16:23.220,0:16:26.420
How I wish Song Zhi would come back

0:16:28.260,0:16:30.260
and tell me that His Majesty didn't like her

0:16:30.820,0:16:32.500
so she was told to leave.

0:16:34.560,0:16:36.060
But if that happens,

0:16:37.920,0:16:39.860
it's not good for the greater plan.

0:16:45.900,0:16:46.760
Go out.

0:16:56.820,0:16:58.540
I appreciate your service.

0:17:00.700,0:17:02.800
I dare not forget my position.

0:17:03.900,0:17:05.180
Speaking of your position,

0:17:06.100,0:17:07.340
I cannot make you feel aggrieved.

0:17:08.600,0:17:10.600
You are Consort Fleur's maid,

0:17:10.660,0:17:12.580
so I need to treat you generously.

0:17:12.620,0:17:13.760
I will make an exception and

0:17:14.120,0:17:15.020
grant you the rank of Companion,

0:17:16.140,0:17:18.380
instead of starting from Escort.

0:17:19.980,0:17:21.400
I thank Your Majesty.

0:17:22.220,0:17:24.060
Remember to kowtow to Consort Flour.

0:17:24.160,0:17:25.860
She was your master after all.

0:17:27.460,0:17:29.680
You should thank her for promoting you.

0:17:31.200,0:17:31.820
Yes.

0:17:57.740,0:17:58.440
Your Highness,

0:17:58.740,0:18:00.780
I've tested - the water temperature is comfortable.

0:18:01.080,0:18:03.080
I've added the rose extract.

0:18:03.200,0:18:05.580
Please allow me to serve
Your Highness as you wash your face.

0:18:40.540,0:18:41.960
You are back.

0:18:42.560,0:18:43.960
Did His Majesty

0:18:43.960,0:18:46.120
give you the rank of Escort?

0:18:49.020,0:18:50.640
His Majesty holds Your Highness in great esteem

0:18:50.920,0:18:51.980
and so, granted me

0:18:52.280,0:18:54.040
the rank of Companion.

0:19:01.940,0:19:04.720
That is quite an honor.

