In the past,

0:24:18.380,0:24:22.980
Consort Fleur would never allow
any maids to get close to His Majesty.

0:24:23.800,0:24:25.060
But today, she ...

0:24:25.220,0:24:26.580
Even she knows that

0:24:27.900,0:24:29.760
today is different from the past.

