Your Majesty,

0:24:43.540,0:24:46.620
This morning His Majesty promoted one of Consort Fleur's maids ...

0:24:47.060,0:24:48.080
to Companion.

0:24:49.140,0:24:52.060
Maids should be promoted to Escort first.

