I consider it against the imperial rules.

0:25:01.540,0:25:03.760
It is the emperors who made the rules.

0:25:04.940,0:25:07.340
There hasn't been a new concubine for a long time.

0:25:07.920,0:25:09.180
Let it be.

0:25:12.340,0:25:13.920
What are you doing?

0:25:14.200,0:25:15.640
Comb my hair carefully!

