0:25:25.820,0:25:27.440
It's already so hot in the morning.

0:25:27.720,0:25:30.120
It will be intolerable by the afternoon.

0:25:30.340,0:25:31.600
You cannot stand the heat, My Lady.

0:25:31.600,0:25:33.140
You can bathe first thing when ...

0:25:37.020,0:25:38.560
Peace to Your Highness.

0:25:47.040,0:25:48.200
Rise.

0:25:50.840,0:25:52.660
Have you ever imagined ...

0:25:53.700,0:25:55.540
the day I have my status restored?

0:25:57.180,0:25:58.960
Your Highness has unending blessings from Heaven.

0:25:59.020,0:26:01.080
I do not question the divine.

0:26:02.280,0:26:04.820
I haven't congratulated Your Highness
on your reinstatement.

0:26:05.360,0:26:06.540
I extend my congratulations.

0:26:06.640,0:26:07.800
No need.

0:26:08.500,0:26:10.760
I do not merit your congratulations.

0:26:12.660,0:26:14.360
The more obediently you behave,

0:26:15.340,0:26:16.960
the more detestable you are.

0:26:17.320,0:26:19.040
Your highness is bantering.

0:26:19.400,0:26:21.220
Does Your Highness prefer me to be defiant

0:26:21.220,0:26:23.380
and speak disrespectfully to Your Highness?

0:26:25.060,0:26:27.080
I dare not offend Your Highness.

0:26:27.460,0:26:29.620
But you have already.

0:26:32.640,0:26:34.820
I will never forget what happened in the past.

0:26:35.840,0:26:37.760
I appreciate Your Highness's advice.

0:26:38.080,0:26:41.260
I am always willing to listen to
Your Highness's teachings.

0:26:42.640,0:26:44.500
You are always willing

0:26:44.980,0:26:47.640
but I don’t want to often see your face.

0:26:49.740,0:26:51.360
Your Highness, please don’t be angry.

0:26:51.360,0:26:52.960
Your Highness's precious health

0:26:52.960,0:26:56.780
is not worth being harmed by a trivial concubine.

0:26:58.240,0:26:59.720
Status and rank are the natural order.

0:26:59.740,0:27:03.880
Why should a noble person be angry with a humble person?

