Isn't this Song Zhi who has
newly gained favor from His Majesty?

0:27:16.580,0:27:18.780
What you just said is true.

0:27:19.560,0:27:21.220
"Status and rank are the natural order."

0:27:21.920,0:27:23.720
You spoke with such confidence

0:27:24.400,0:27:26.500
that it is a shame

0:27:26.780,0:27:28.660
that you’re just a humble Companion.

