Your Highness,

0:27:39.640,0:27:43.420
His Majesty invited us to the opera house.

0:27:43.960,0:27:45.020
I’ve heard that

0:27:45.080,0:27:48.720
His Majesty specially ordered Your Highness's
favorite play, The Niangzi Pass.

0:27:49.160,0:27:51.100
Why bother wasting time

0:27:51.520,0:27:53.680
under the scorching sun?

0:28:13.780,0:28:15.180
Vermilion, let’s go.

0:28:20.340,0:28:22.780
It was getting hot outside and you hadn’t come back.

0:28:22.840,0:28:24.620
I was about to send someone to look.

0:28:25.160,0:28:26.900
I was just walking around in the garden.

0:28:27.280,0:28:28.540
What can happen?

0:28:29.800,0:28:31.940
Jade, I was furious.

0:28:32.220,0:28:34.660
We ran into Consort Fleur and Companion Zhi.

0:28:35.000,0:28:36.620
My Lady suffered a great grievance.

0:28:36.940,0:28:38.260
What happened?

0:28:38.540,0:28:40.320
My Lady is in high favor right now.

0:28:40.440,0:28:42.260
How could they not be fearful of behaving rudely?

0:28:42.300,0:28:44.200
Consort Fleur always treats My Lady like that.

0:28:44.380,0:28:45.840
But Companion Zhi is intolerable!

0:28:46.160,0:28:47.400
She was just a maid.

0:28:47.400,0:28:49.020
How dare she "speak with barbs"!

0:28:49.520,0:28:51.360
She was Consort Fleur’s servant.

0:28:51.660,0:28:53.940
Naturally, she has became a jackal relying on a tiger.

0:28:54.080,0:28:55.800
My Lady, you were being too kind.

0:28:55.800,0:28:57.420
We can ignore Consort Fleur,

0:28:57.420,0:28:59.320
but do we need to tolerate Song Zhi?

0:28:59.560,0:29:00.840
If I were you,

0:29:00.840,0:29:03.340
I would slap her so sharply

0:29:03.420,0:29:05.620
and tell His Majesty to banish her to the slave caste.

0:29:06.120,0:29:07.540
Just listen to Vermillion -

0:29:07.640,0:29:09.260
her tongue has become so unsparing.

0:29:10.380,0:29:12.380
It seems that she is in charge of my palace.

0:29:13.060,0:29:14.820
Your temper is too short.

0:29:15.640,0:29:17.720
Can that accomplsh anything for me?

0:29:18.640,0:29:19.980
I told you both:

0:29:19.980,0:29:21.540
don't cause conflicts with Confort Fleur.

0:29:21.580,0:29:23.100
Now one more rule:

0:29:23.100,0:29:24.740
don't cause conflicts with her subjects.

0:29:25.260,0:29:26.440
Pay no attention to them.

0:29:26.560,0:29:28.420
There is ample time ahead for us.

0:29:28.960,0:29:30.940
But Song Zhi treated you so impertinently,

0:29:31.040,0:29:32.700
do you forgive her, My Lady?

0:29:32.720,0:29:34.120
Jade, what do you think?

0:29:35.060,0:29:36.160
My Lady,

0:29:36.740,0:29:38.500
I believe it's better to endure this momentarily

0:29:38.600,0:29:39.780
for future revenge.

0:29:39.820,0:29:41.800
Forbearance is a must at the moment.

0:29:41.940,0:29:44.540
Besides, I disdain taking action against someone like Song Zhi.

0:29:45.800,0:29:47.100
Enduring her now

0:29:47.260,0:29:49.260
doesn't mean I will not act in the future.

0:29:50.060,0:29:52.200
Song Zhi dares to be so arrogant

0:29:52.440,0:29:54.340
because she has Consort Fleur behind her.

0:29:54.760,0:29:56.820
Do you really think her capable of anything?

0:29:56.940,0:29:58.680
She's just a small pawn.

0:29:59.720,0:30:01.180
My Lady, you mean…

0:30:01.740,0:30:05.160
What is written in Du Fu’s
sixth poem in “Out of the Frontier”?

0:30:06.960,0:30:10.280
"To capture an army, shoot their horses.
And to take down an enemy, ..."

0:30:12.980,0:30:14.760
"eliminate their ruler!"

0:30:17.600,0:30:18.940
I have read

0:30:19.700,0:30:23.880
all these memorandums are to impeach Nian Gengyao.

0:30:24.420,0:30:26.900
I have marked and commented on each of them.

0:30:27.920,0:30:28.760
Yes.

0:30:28.900,0:30:31.040
I await Your Majesty's adjudication.

0:30:31.880,0:30:34.000
Nian Gengyao acts arrogantly

0:30:34.720,0:30:37.180
and naturally the other officials resent him.

0:30:38.620,0:30:39.560
I

0:30:40.000,0:30:41.280
as the Emperor

0:30:41.420,0:30:44.320
must listen to the officials and the people.

0:30:45.140,0:30:46.780
Naturally, I want them

0:30:47.500,0:30:49.300
to be able to speak freely.

0:30:50.240,0:30:51.300
Zhen Yuandao.

0:30:51.640,0:30:52.900
Your Majesty.

0:30:53.380,0:30:55.520
Those who are able to speak -

0:30:55.680,0:30:58.840
make sure they open their mouths to you.

0:30:59.420,0:31:00.680
Yes, My Majesty.

