Two days ago,

0:31:02.880,0:31:05.560
I asked Nian Gengyao about something important.

0:31:07.140,0:31:08.020
Of course,

0:31:08.140,0:31:10.240
I also want to hear your opinions.

0:31:10.560,0:31:11.740
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:31:12.320,0:31:15.800
Lord VIII Yunsi and Lord IX Yuntang 
[the Emperor's brothers]

0:31:15.940,0:31:18.900
have long been imprisioned in Imperial Clan Court.

0:31:19.540,0:31:22.800
I've heard they not only didn't reflect on their faults

0:31:23.460,0:31:25.820
but also cursed me, and the prior emperor.

0:31:26.860,0:31:29.860
What do you think I should do?

0:31:30.120,0:31:33.280
The guilty officials Yunsi and Yuntang
formed a faction and acted unlawfully.

0:31:33.540,0:31:35.300
If they refuse to be repentant,

0:31:35.340,0:31:37.940
that is an unforgivable crime.

0:31:40.100,0:31:41.980
Uncle, what do you think?

0:31:42.600,0:31:45.760
Your Majesty, although Yunsi and Yuntang are guilty,

0:31:45.960,0:31:47.900
they are, after all,

0:31:47.920,0:31:49.440
Your Majesty's brothers.

0:31:49.440,0:31:53.920
What about sending respected senior members of
the clan to enlighten them in Imperial Clan Court?

0:31:55.700,0:31:56.860
Zhen Yuandao.

0:31:56.900,0:32:00.520
Your Majesty, if they dare to ignore
the relations of monarch and subject

0:32:00.680,0:32:03.220
as Your Majesty's brothers,

0:32:03.340,0:32:06.440
or if they formerly failed to fulfil the duties between brothers

0:32:06.460,0:32:09.160
and refuse to repent and amend their faults,

0:32:09.980,0:32:13.680
then Your Majesty need not grant any favors beyond the laws.

0:32:21.300,0:32:24.260
All your comments are reasoned.

0:32:26.080,0:32:27.780
I will think it over.

0:32:31.720,0:32:34.860
His Majesty asked my brother
what to do about Yunsi and Yuntang.

0:32:35.700,0:32:36.980
What do you think?

0:32:37.380,0:32:39.620
The great general has been repeatedly impugned recently,

0:32:39.680,0:32:40.980
and His Majesty ...

0:32:42.120,0:32:44.180
expressed approval of the accusers.

0:32:44.440,0:32:47.200
I'm afraid the general might be uneasy about this,

0:32:47.460,0:32:50.400
and fearful of offending His Majesty
with an improper response.

0:32:52.960,0:32:54.700
So at this juncture,

0:32:54.920,0:32:56.900
he must be careful how he answers His Majesty.

0:32:57.100,0:32:58.020
Yes.

0:32:58.280,0:32:59.260
If His Majesty

0:32:59.500,0:33:02.340
shows no mercy towards
his brothers Yunsi and Yuntang,

0:33:03.940,0:33:06.660
what would happen if my brother was slandered in the future?

0:33:07.600,0:33:09.540
Would His Majesty be even more ruthless?

0:33:10.160,0:33:11.840
Your Highness is having unnecessary concerns.

0:33:11.880,0:33:14.580
Why would His Majesty do this to the great general?

0:33:16.280,0:33:19.380
There have been so many people speaking against my brother lately.

0:33:19.980,0:33:21.700
Even among the people surrounding my brother -

0:33:22.040,0:33:23.680
some ingrates have appeared.

0:33:24.440,0:33:28.020
His Majesty asked my brother
such a question in this situation ...

0:33:29.920,0:33:31.860
What does he really mean?

0:33:32.460,0:33:33.660
Perhaps...

0:33:34.140,0:33:36.920
Perhaps His Majesty just asked casually, that's all.

0:33:37.240,0:33:38.240
No chance.

0:33:39.400,0:33:41.080
His Majesty is never like that.

0:33:41.720,0:33:43.660
His Majesty always thought highly of my brother.

0:33:44.040,0:33:46.200
But now, begins to doubt my brother.

0:33:48.500,0:33:50.760
The Nians are always loyal and devoted to His Majesty.

0:33:50.940,0:33:51.660
Yes.

0:33:51.660,0:33:53.620
His Majesty must be confused by the rumors.

0:33:54.620,0:33:57.480
His Majesty is not a person who
feels no affection for the past.

0:33:57.620,0:34:00.260
If Your Highness is afraid that
"teeth will feel cold when the lips are gone",

0:34:00.260,0:34:01.520
Your Highness could ask the great general

0:34:01.560,0:34:04.420
to talk more about etiquette and filial piety
in front of His Majesty

0:34:04.580,0:34:06.700
in order to appeal to His Majesty emotionally.

0:34:06.940,0:34:08.340
This will remind His Majesty

0:34:08.440,0:34:10.360
of the great general's loyalty

0:34:10.520,0:34:12.940
and create gratitude for his military merits.

0:34:15.120,0:34:18.060
But Yunsi and Yuntang fought against 
His Majesty for the throne

0:34:18.520,0:34:20.800
and intended to destabilize His Majesty's authority.

0:34:21.580,0:34:22.780
They are

0:34:23.180,0:34:25.240
the ones His Majesty hates and detests the most.

0:34:27.520,0:34:29.340
Is it all right to reply this way?

0:34:30.740,0:34:31.760
Of course,

0:34:31.800,0:34:35.020
the great general should not advise
His Majesty to release Yunsi and Yuntang.

0:34:35.820,0:34:36.880
However,

0:34:37.040,0:34:40.760
there is no harm in mentioning their 
decades of devotion as brothers.

0:34:40.960,0:34:44.220
And at the same time, asserting his own loyalty to His Majesty.

0:34:44.940,0:34:47.660
I believe such a reply would be fine.

0:34:55.040,0:34:57.380
This is not a bad concession.

0:34:59.720,0:35:02.100
His Majesty is soft-hearted and affectionate towards the past

0:35:02.280,0:35:04.100
with Your Highness,

0:35:04.180,0:35:06.940
and even more so with the great general.

0:35:30.680,0:35:33.020
You are the most carefree in the palace.

0:35:33.920,0:35:35.460
Grace to Your Majesty.

0:35:42.100,0:35:44.920
I have nothing to do. I'm just being lazy.

0:35:45.160,0:35:47.100
Did His Majesty come from the Governance Hall?

0:35:49.000,0:35:50.900
Consort Fleur just came to me.

0:35:51.820,0:35:53.720
To speak for General Nian?

0:35:55.240,0:35:56.920
She came to speak about you.

0:35:58.480,0:36:01.620
Of course, I know you have done your best to tolerate it.

0:36:03.440,0:36:05.980
Your Majesty won't believe in what she said, right?

0:36:07.740,0:36:08.980
I won't.

0:36:10.180,0:36:12.060
Consort Fleur told me that you were disrespectful to her.

0:36:12.260,0:36:15.160
She also brought Companion Zhi
who was crying endlessly.

0:36:15.480,0:36:19.120
It's her nature to be strong-willed and
she never stops until she reaches her goal.

0:36:20.320,0:36:22.520
What does Your Majesty intend to do about it?

0:36:36.500,0:36:39.860
I have to make this move against my will.

0:36:41.180,0:36:44.580
I don't want you to hear these
disturbing things and worry about me.

0:36:45.080,0:36:46.840
I tell you only that

0:36:47.180,0:36:49.700
Nian Gengyao is getting more and more presumptuous.

0:36:50.160,0:36:51.880
I have no more tolerance for it.

0:36:53.480,0:36:56.480
Your Majesty is the Son of Heaven.
You're capable of doing anything.

0:36:57.000,0:36:59.180
Since the knife has been in your heart for a long time,

0:36:59.180,0:37:00.680
it's time to remove it.

0:37:01.100,0:37:04.720
I have refrained until this moment
in order to remove it smoothly.

0:37:05.280,0:37:07.620
If you were me, would you do the same?

0:37:08.920,0:37:11.020
Yes, I understand Your Majesty.

0:37:12.180,0:37:13.360
Good.

0:37:13.840,0:37:16.700
It's still early, I'll go back to read the memorandum.

0:37:17.140,0:37:18.640
You can have some rest.

0:37:22.040,0:37:23.800
I bid Your Majesty goodbye.

0:37:27.460,0:37:28.420
Tomorrow,

0:37:28.580,0:37:30.680
I will host a banquet in Jiuzhou Qingyan.

0:37:30.960,0:37:32.060
Go there early.

0:37:32.300,0:37:33.320
Yes, Your Majesty.

0:37:38.440,0:37:39.560
Your Highness,

0:37:39.640,0:37:42.200
tonight, His Majesty selected
the name tag of Companion Zhi again.

0:37:43.400,0:37:44.580
You can go now.

0:37:44.580,0:37:45.700
Yes, Your Highness.

0:37:45.940,0:37:48.100
Did you hear that?

0:37:48.660,0:37:50.640
His Majesty is favoring Companion Zhi again.

0:37:50.640,0:37:53.020
Has it been any different in the past few days?

0:37:53.280,0:37:56.460
His Majesty has a new favorite.
He is only in the mood for her.

0:37:56.860,0:37:58.780
What kind of a new favorite is she?

0:37:58.980,0:38:00.760
She was just a humble servant before,

0:38:00.800,0:38:03.080
but now she's climbed into the dragon's bed.

0:38:03.240,0:38:04.280
It disgusts me

0:38:04.460,0:38:06.780
when I think about how she soils His Majesty's bed.

0:38:07.000,0:38:08.760
Sourire, you're being frank and outspoken.

0:38:09.080,0:38:11.320
I wouldn't dare to say this out loud.

0:38:11.540,0:38:13.120
I'm speaking the truth.

0:38:13.120,0:38:15.940
Since I dare to say it,
I'm not afraid of anyone spreading it.

0:38:17.320,0:38:19.880
Someday I will turn this "newly favored" to "out of favor".

0:38:20.220,0:38:21.980
Then she will learn her lesson.

0:38:30.400,0:38:31.640
Your Majesty,

0:38:31.820,0:38:34.720
I heard that you don’t like Great General Nian recently,

0:38:34.920,0:38:37.240
and have criticized his memorandums.

0:38:38.980,0:38:40.900
Who told you this?

0:38:41.400,0:38:43.360
I dare not listen to any gossip.

0:38:43.660,0:38:46.500
It's just because I live with Consort Fleur

0:38:46.660,0:38:48.600
and always hear such talk.

0:38:49.300,0:38:50.840
What are they talking about?

0:38:51.240,0:38:55.520
Do they say I'm unfaithful in my favors,
to rebuke a meritorious official?

0:38:55.880,0:38:57.200
Of course not.

0:38:57.280,0:38:59.640
They say that Great General Nian's conduct is improper,

0:38:59.940,0:39:01.480
which upsets Your Majesty.

0:39:01.600,0:39:05.800
I am angry because I think highly of Nian Gengyao.

0:39:06.320,0:39:08.540
I expect him to do everything well,

0:39:08.820,0:39:11.780
and not give others a reason to talk
and cause trouble for me.

0:39:12.880,0:39:15.400
So it's because Your Majesty cherishes the great general.

0:39:16.340,0:39:19.020
I cherish Consort Fleur and you.

0:39:20.160,0:39:22.360
Nian Gengyao contributed to the state.

0:39:22.840,0:39:24.680
And he's also my brother-in-law.

0:39:25.840,0:39:28.380
Consort Fleur has served me for years,

0:39:28.900,0:39:31.820
and she guides you to be sweet and well-behaved.

0:39:33.180,0:39:35.020
I hold it dearly in my heart.

0:39:37.360,0:39:38.700
Your Majesty.

0:39:44.740,0:39:47.640
My brother handed in a memorandum
following my suggestion.

0:39:47.760,0:39:49.300
His Majesty didn't say anything.

0:39:50.440,0:39:52.880
But His Majesty has stopped reprimanding my brother.

0:39:52.980,0:39:55.680
That's good. I feel relieved, too.

0:39:56.900,0:39:58.500
You have no idea.

0:39:58.780,0:40:02.280
I heard every day how His Majesty
reprimanded my brother in his memorandums.

0:40:02.620,0:40:04.980
It sent thousands of shivers through my heart.

0:40:05.880,0:40:09.440
Fortunately, Song Zhi has been serving His Majesty.

0:40:09.900,0:40:11.600
From His Majesty's tone,

0:40:11.800,0:40:13.140
she sounded out that

0:40:13.260,0:40:16.240
His Majesty still recognizes my brother's
great contributions to the nation.

0:40:16.480,0:40:17.460
Yes.

0:40:17.480,0:40:19.320
I can finally feel relieved.

0:40:20.600,0:40:22.420
His Majesty reprimanded the great general

0:40:22.480,0:40:24.880
only because of the base persons
seeking trouble from nothing.

0:40:24.880,0:40:26.580
His Majesty had to make a gesture.

0:40:26.920,0:40:29.820
How can His  Majesty really reprimand the great general?

0:40:31.940,0:40:33.980
Your method worked fairly well.

0:40:34.440,0:40:36.260
As long as His Majesty sees the memorandum

0:40:36.500,0:40:38.240
and favors Your Highness more,

0:40:38.420,0:40:40.380
my mind will be at peace.

0:40:40.500,0:40:42.000
You are very conscientious.

0:40:42.340,0:40:45.180
As long as His Majesty favors me and my brother as before,

0:40:45.600,0:40:47.520
I won't treat you unfavorably.

0:40:48.680,0:40:50.880
On the day when Wenyi comes of age,

0:40:51.480,0:40:54.680
I will ask His Majesty to grant you the title of Concubine.

0:40:58.520,0:41:01.180
Your Highness, Companion Zhi has come back.

0:41:01.860,0:41:04.680
She wishes to pay her respects to Your Highness.

0:41:05.180,0:41:06.480
It's all right.

0:41:06.820,0:41:08.320
Let her take a rest first.

0:41:08.320,0:41:09.380
Yes, Your Highness.

0:41:09.380,0:41:10.420
Wait.

0:41:13.980,0:41:16.420
Don’t forget to reward her the ginseng soup.

0:41:18.580,0:41:20.040
Y..Yes, Your Highness.

0:41:23.380,0:41:26.280
Companion Zhi served His Majesty again last night.

0:41:26.680,0:41:28.300
With Your Highness's guidance,

0:41:28.440,0:41:31.300
Companion Zhi has certainly
gained high favor with His Majesty.

0:41:31.440,0:41:33.340
This is also her own good fortune.

0:41:34.120,0:41:35.900
You have my guidance just the same,

0:41:36.100,0:41:38.160
yet you are not favored as she is.

0:41:40.120,0:41:42.420
These few days, however,

0:41:42.760,0:41:45.120
a few gusts of wind blew into my ears.

0:41:45.940,0:41:50.820
I heard that Concubine Souire is very dissatisfied with
Companion Zhi's new-found favor.

0:41:51.420,0:41:54.380
I've also heard a bit about this from His Majesty.

0:41:55.420,0:41:58.020
No wonder His Majesty hasn't visited her recently.

0:41:59.040,0:42:00.540
Now I understand why.

0:42:00.740,0:42:03.780
His Majesty desires only Song Zhi.

0:42:03.960,0:42:07.720
Why would His Majesty want to hear
Concubine Souire's words soured with jealousy?

0:42:08.960,0:42:10.160
All right.

0:42:13.480,0:42:14.960
If she has been feeling sour,

0:42:16.500,0:42:17.760
I will

0:42:18.540,0:42:20.360
turn her favor sour to match.

